name: Up Rising Tee - Black
description:
Sometimes we just gotta question what is in front of us. We cannot just absorb in whatever the government limits us to.  We must stand for justice and rebel for what is right.

Featuring our HW logo on the left sleeve, this tee is available in Black only.

name: Destroy and Rebuild Tee - Black
description:
All the designs and directions that we make for our label goes through many phases. We found that sometimes looking at the same thing over and over just goes nowhere. You just gotta step back, scrap the initial design and start fresh. Hence, destroy and rebuild.

Featuring our HW logo on the left sleeve, this tee is available in Black only.

name: Mobb'N Deep II Tee - Black
description:
Although the recent crisis in Syria has settled down for now, we still feel the need to draw attention to the matter of humanity. This revision of our Mobb’n Deep design shows how powerful the public can be when we are aware of what is going on in the world. Are you ready to join the murder, rise up, and mobb deep?

Featuring our HW logo on the left sleeve, this tee is available in Black only.

name: Murder Over Everything Tee - Black
description:
“Blood makes you related, Loyalty makes you family.” Join the Murder.

Featuring our HW logo on the left sleeve, this tee is available in Black only.

name: Destroy and Prevail Tee - Red/ Niners
description:
Playing with typography, we were able to change the classic ampersand by adding a bow and arrow to it. 

Specifically made for the Niner’s season, the shirt has SF printed on the back with niner’s gold. Featuring our HW logo on the left sleeve, this tee is available in Red.

name: Destroy and Prevail Tee - Black/ Teal
description:
Playing with typography, we were able to change the classic ampersand by adding a bow and arrow to it. 

Featuring our HW logo on the left sleeve, this tee is available in Black with Teal print.

name: MURDER Est. Tee - Black
description:
Since the conception of Halloway, we have always wanted to put out an ambigram design where the word can be read upside-down. So here it is, the design reads Murder one way and also reads Redrum the other.

This tee has a front left chest design with our Feather logo and an oversized back design, available in Black only.

name: Visionaries Tee - Black
description:
Ever see movies or scenes where the grim reaper shows the soul how their life could have been if they chose a different path? If you have, you’ll know why we labeled this as the Visionaries tee.

This pocket tee features our HLWY Cross logo on the front left chest, our HW logo on the left sleeve, and oversize back design. Available in Black only.

name: Catch 22 Tee - Olive
description:
When a bomb is about to be dropped, there is nowhere to hide. Either way you’re f*cked. Man up and face the situation.

Featuring our HW logo on the left sleeve, this tee is available in Black, and Olive.

name: Catch 22 Tee - Black
description:

name: Clique Bang Murder Tee - Charcoal
description:
With this pun intended design, we wanted to capture a visual connotation of different social groups.

This tee has a front left chest design and an oversized back design. Featuring our HW logo on the left sleeve, this tee is available in Black, and Charcoal Grey.

name: I Like 'Em Tee - Black
description:
"I like 'em brown, yellow, Puerto Rican, or Haitian. Name is Phife Dawg from the Zulu Nation..." 

This design is a tribute to the classic Hip-Hop track, Electric Relaxation by A Tribe Called Quest. Over here at Halloway, we are highly influenced by hip-hop music, especially the classics of ATCQ. Now you can wear this shirt to any hip-hop concerts and have a fellow Tribe enthusiast finish off the line! Featuring our HW logo on the left sleeve, this tee is available in Black, Royal Blue, and Red.

name: Classic Gradient Tank - Black
description: Here is our Classic Logo with a nice gradient fade from teal to purple. The color way fits perfectly for this Summer! Available in both Black and Grey Tank-tops.

name: Hiatus Tee - Black
description: The Hiatus Tee is our favorite design from this Summer's collection, which is why we titled the drop after it. We believe after all the hard work everyone goes through, we all deserve a little time off from the daily grind to enjoy life. The graphic shows 3 polaroids from a little Hawaiian getaway, each with something very memorable to take away with. We hope you all will be able to take some time off to enjoy your Summer and make some memories of your own. Featuring our HW logo on the left sleeve, this tee is available in both Black and Heather Grey.

name: Internationally Infamous Tee - White
description: Traveling the world and learning about different cultures has always been a goal of Halloway's. With this design, we have travelled to a few countries to show their infamous facts and got our passport stamps as proof! Featuring our HW logo on the left sleeve, this tee is available in White with multi-colored print and Black with white print.

name: Big Worm Tee - Black
description: This worm graphic simply stands for "the early bird catches the worm." In this industry and any other in general, everything is about being on-time and meeting deadlines. Hand drawn by our in-house artist, Nate, this piece is to remind us to not procrastinate and always stay hungry. Featuring our HW logo on the left sleeve, this tee is available in Black and Heather Grey.
